FireResist 5

Boiling Blood (Su)
Any creature damaging you with a non-reach piercing or slashing weapon takes 1d4 fire damage on each successful hit.

Flaming Weapon (Su)
Free action: Ignite weapon, adding 1d6 fire damage.
Stacks with existing fire damage from same weapon.

Smoke Breath (Su)
Swift action: Breath a cloud of poisonous smoke, 5ft radius.
Dissipates at beginning of your next turn.
A moderate wind disperses the smoke (11+ mph)
Creatures beginning their turn in the smoke make DC13+ConMod Fort save vs Sickened 1 round.
Successful save grants immunity for 24 hours.


